      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Grabbin\u0027 Life by the Horns",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Sup, Ace! Just got a quest to\r\nhunt a Rajang acting gnarly out\r\nin the Jungle. Wanna get in on\r\nthis thrashin\u0027 action? I know you\r\ndo! That\u0027s why your my favorite\r\npupil! You never say no to a chance\r\nto thrash on some monsters!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rajang",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Prendre le taureau par les cornes",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "L\u0027artiste ! Tu tombes \u00E0 pic !\r\nTu peux m\u0027aider \u00E0 chasser un\r\nRajang dans la Jungle ? Il\r\nfaut que je m\u0027occupe de \u00E7a au\r\nplus vite... parce que. On est\r\nle duo ultime, aucun monstre\r\nnous r\u00E9siste !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rajang",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Alimentato da rabbia dorata",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "Che tempismo perfetto! Puoi\r\naiutarmi a cacciare un Rajang\r\napparso nella giungla? Devo\r\noccuparmene al pi\u00F9 presto\r\nper... vari motivi. Ma noi\r\nsiamo la miglior squadra che\r\nesista! Non sar\u00E0 un problema.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rajang",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Immer dabei",
        "Client": "Meister Utsushi",
        "Description": "Hey, Ass! Ich habe gerade eine\r\nQuest bekommen, einen Rajang\r\nzu jagen, der sich im Dschungel\r\nkrass auff\u00FChrt. Bist du dabei?\r\nNat\u00FCrlich bist du dabei!\r\nWenn es darum geht, Monster zu\r\nverpr\u00FCgeln, bist du immer dabei!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Rajang.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Coge al Rajang por los cuernos",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "\u00A1Llegas justo a tiempo, hacha!\r\nAcaba de llegar una misi\u00F3n para\r\nmachacar a un Rajang que est\u00E1\r\nli\u00E1ndola en la Jungla.\r\n\u00BFQu\u00E9 te parece? \u00A1S\u00E9 que t\u00FA te\r\nencargar\u00E1s, t\u00FA nunca dices que\r\nno a machacar monstruos!",
